      • keyDescriptor

        public static com.google.protobuf.Descriptors.FieldDescriptor keyDescriptor(com.google.protobuf.Descriptors.FieldDescriptor field)

        The descriptor type is Descriptors.FieldDescriptor because the map key technically is the field of the ...Entry message type.
